{
  "stem": "27509.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And even at Pesach time, he refused to have the little bit of bread that was given them daily because he wouldn't eat bread on Pesach.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So-- and there are stories being-- that, that were told to me here about how his endurance in jail gave all the people there a, a feeling of strength to, to endure what they were enduring because of the-- of the inner strength of these men.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The, the people-- the jailers pleaded with him that he should eat because they said, you will die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You won't survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You want survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Nothing doing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He used to, at Pesach time, exchange his piece of bread with somebody's bit of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So he ate the potatoes, which was possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But he wouldn't eat the bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He came out there, it was skin and bones, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But he survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And that is how, how they-- they survived the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And that is-- and I was, from Shanghai afterwards, corresponding with mother and father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It took nine months for such a letter to make the around-the-world trip, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And I used to write to them in Russian so that the Russian censor could read it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Otherwise, it would have never got to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "My Russian was somewhat less than perfect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But they most probably had a good chuckles in reading it, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I, I did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I used to get replies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I've got some reply cards from them, yellow, brownish open cards from them in Russian of, of those years-- I've got in my possession.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course we knew about the collapse of France and the low countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to the extent to which it was at all possible, we knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
